dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Contour interval 20 feet.
Gettysburg, Fairfield, Emmitsburg, and Taneytown atlas sheets combined in this map.
Surveyed in 1885 and 1906-1909 in cooperation with the states of Pennsylvania and Maryland.
